@Lovinity ah, thanks for the clarification. I see the leak now. It seems to be related to sending the IPC event over `contextBridge`.

Here's an updated gist with a commented-out modification in preload.js which, if swapped in, results in no leakage. https://gist.github.com/1c4bffaf558fbec5bf7b6de98009968b

